column5: I think I understand now.  Yes, I was smiling. Sometimes,it just dosent show. LOL
Depends who was behind the camera  You can only smile so many times at Terry.
Probably true, but we laugh at with him all the time!

you ever wonder if a fish sees your lure hanging off a downrigger in 100ft of water going 2 mph on lake simcoe  yeah I wonder too  I didnt see fish but I could see the lure     https://youtu.be/wCa-4099AOI
With our pleasant smiles Brian, we could pass for twins.
Your getting the hang of it bud. .  Very cool.  We just need to work on not getting wrapped up on all three lines. DOH  Me bad for getting you broke off today.
With our pleasant smiles Brian, we could pass for twins.    Lew,I see the smile. It,s all about the stach.
hahaha great photos boys. I thought Bill looked far more gruff than Lew ever did...until Lew posted his pic.
aagh its the moustache .I finally fingered it out. lew your secrets safe with me.
They don't smile anymore after catching the mother load  of fish!   they have no energy left way to go, keep smiling!
